subject: Hello,..
body:
Hello,..
 This is Mr Jamie Dimon, CEO JPMorgan Chase Bank, NY, USA. I am sure
you’ve been seeing my text and Email but I really don't know exactly
why you’ve been ignoring.
 The JPMorgan Chase Bank, N.Y, USA has approved to complete the
Delivery of $7 Million Dollars and 2023 Mercedes Benz from the Federal
Government as Compensation Reward.
 The Funds has been validated to be delivered Via an ATM Card which
your're expected to response back within 24 hours and provide your
Residence details to avoid wrong registration process;..

subject: Re: Hello,..
body:
Hello Mr. Jamie Dimon,

Wow, that sounds like an amazing opportunity! I'm really excited to hear more about this. Can you please tell me more about how this reward program works? And why was I selected for such a generous gift?

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Mary
